    Promoter:   pGhSCW-late (549 bp)
    Gene:       TYRP1 (1614 bp)
    Terminator: tNOS (253 bp)
    Total:      2416 bp
    Function:   Stabilizes melanin intermediates. Prevents toxic accumulation of dopaquinone by channeling it toward eumelanin.

