    Promoter:   pGhSCW-late (549 bp)
    Gene:       DCT (1560 bp)
    Terminator: tNOS (253 bp)
    Total:      2362 bp
    Function:   Converts dopachrome to DHICA, improving melanin polymer quality and ensuring deep black color (vs. brown).

